::KitKat::

She stood up and looked at the rat she had been holding on to since 
the battle.  It was a little shaken up, no damage. She shook her 
head.  She couldn' fathom why a mouse would hold on to a rat like she 
had been.  She opened her link, "Scorponok, the enemy bots have 
departed.  Did you find the mouse yet?"
